{"tid":1916620,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"黄之鋒聯同陳嘉朗出九西","createTime":"2020-03-09T03:40:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T11:27:15.000Z","uid":389,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c594658ff0b65b1d94e466b2f07f3d9d1be4072a","tid":1916620,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:40:30.000Z","msg":"日前流傳黃之鋒有意聯合梁凱晴出選九龍東挑戰泛民第三席，黃之鋒一直不置可否，網上質疑梁凱晴能力留言甚囂塵上，九龍東立會戰線如火如荼之際，九西或再現變天。黃之鋒貼文表示日前聯同尖少咀西區議員陳嘉朗以國際戰線出訪重慶大廈。現時九龍西泛民有意者甚多，有傳劉小麗、曾健超、李傲然、何啟明、余德寶及劉偉聰等均有意角逐、以上屆九西投票分佈，建制只能穩套兩位，但若泛民本土不能協調，或會流失第四席，所以泛民如何協調將成勝敗關健。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YiLORQG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYiLORQG.jpg&h=decc8f5f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a8992377fabfbc7eeb2cf7313af6ff136255b04","tid":1916620,"uid":13918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:41:53.000Z","msg":"標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24aad371b35776bf5b6f2f4b53a47b9a968d9ad3","tid":1916620,"uid":389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8a8992377fabfbc7eeb2cf7313af6ff136255b04","tid":1916620,"uid":13918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:41:53.000Z","msg":"標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:42:26.000Z","msg":"？？<br />\n無呃人喎"},{"pid":"459edd102c8f830163512dd6d2941f40f94e6b78","tid":1916620,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:43:10.000Z","msg":"G phone個蛋撻頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca79be1775205a358a1cf45c3196cb9f7f4fbe41","tid":1916620,"uid":131064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:43:57.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">樓豬好憎陳嘉朗</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"0951804ac66e69564